    "en": {
      "title": "Dan's brother is murdered",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Wellampitiya Police, two unknown persons carrying sharp weapons on a motorcycle hacked a person to death near the Orugudawatta Flyover yesterday (25th) night.",
        "Prakas Thilina Kumara, 34, resident of Kalansuriya Lane, Wellampitiya, Methotamulla, has been murdered.",
        "Police also say that the murdered person is the brother of social activist Dan Priyasad.",
        "The police say that the murdered person, who usually stays near the Orugudawatta flyover in the evening with his friends, is on judicial bail from remand for causing serious injuries to several people with sharp weapons.",
        "A police officer said that an accused appears at the Wellampitiya Police on the last Sunday of every month on court orders.",
        "On the instructions of Wellampitiya Police Station Chief Inspector Nilantha Indika, a team including Crime Division Station Officer Sub Inspector Viraj is conducting investigations."
      ],
